# Solicitation Summary: FA940126Q0001 — Aircrew Facility Support

---

## Solicitation Overview
- **Title:** Aircrew Facility Support
- **Solicitation Number:** FA940126Q0001
- **Issuing Organization:** Department of the Air Force, 377th Air Base Wing (AFGSC), 377 MSG/Contracting Division – Kirtland AFB, New Mexico
- **Product Service Code:** S216 (Facility Support Services)
- **NAICS Code:** 561210 – Facility Support Services
- **Size Standard:** $47 Million
- **Set Aside:** 100% Service-Disabled Veteran Owned Small Business (SDVOSB) IAW FAR 19.1405(b)

## Description
Solicitation seeks support for **Aircrew Facility Support** services at Kirtland Air Force Base, NM. Scope and requirements are detailed in Attachment 1 – Performance Work Statement (PWS) dated 22 October 2025.

## Deadlines
- **Question Deadline:** 30 October 2025, 5:00 PM (MDT/MST)
- **Quote Submission Deadline:** 14 November 2025, 4:00 PM (MDT/MST)
    - (*Note: Previous deadlines were 10 & 12 November; use 14 November as final extended deadline.*)
- **Quote Validity:** 90 days

