## Instructions & Requirements
- **Eligibility:** 100% SDVOSB set-aside; compliance with NAICS and size standards mandatory.
- **Submission Instructions:**
    - Email quotes in .pdf, .doc, or .xls formats (<30MB) to both POCs (emails above).
    - Do not use .zip or restricted formats.
- **Quote Content:**
    - Clear, concise, substantive—avoid marketing/ad content.
    - Identify exceptions to terms with rationale.
- **Required Factors:**
    1. **Technical:** 5–6 page technical plan referencing Attachment 1 (PWS).
    2. **Price:** Fill out Annex 1 for all CLINs, TEP includes options.
    3. **Mission Essential Plan:** As per DFARS 252.237-7024, specific to requirements.

## Additional Notes
- This is an RFQ. Only formal quotes are requested—no separate written solicitation will be issued.
- **Funds are not currently available;** award pending funding. The Government may cancel the solicitation without cost to proposers.
- Wage and labor details per Attachment 4 and NM Gross Receipts Overview ([link](https://www.tax.newmexico.gov/businesses/gross-receipts-overview/)).

